columns.name: Copay_Color_Mapping
columns.description:
This field helps in visually distinguishing patients based on the amount they are expected to pay after assistance or insurance
Low Copay - Green, representing patients with the least out-of-pocket expenses after assistance.
Moderate Copay - Yellow, signifying a mid-range copay.
High Copay - Red or On Hold, indicating higher out-of-pocket costs, potentially due to fewer assistance options or higher-tier services.
